---
import QuotationMark from "../../assets/quotation-mark.svg";
import CTAButton from "../CTAButton.astro";
---

<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center mb-[var(--join-connect-header-offset)]">
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-evenly pt-24">
    <div class="text-center text-2xl font-light mb-12 md:mb-0 md:mr-6 drop-shadow-lg md:max-w-[40%]">
      <p class="mb-4">Dan Heuertz has been an entrepreneur for almost 4 decades, starting businesses ranging from bars and restaurants to salt mines and payment processing.</p>
      <p class="font-semibold">After having seen and done it all, he wanted to share his experiences and frameworks with other entrepreneurs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center text-2xl font-light md:ml-6 drop-shadow-lg md:max-w-[40%] border border-gray-300 rounded-lg relative p-4 shadow-lg">
      <QuotationMark id="leftQuote" fill="currentColor" transform="scale(-1,-1)" class="absolute -left-4 -top-4" />
      <p class="mb-4">
        For years, I tried writing a book until a health crisis in 2021 pushed me to hire a ghostwriter. But after going through that process,
        <span class="font-semibold">my voice was lost.</span>
      </p>
      <p>
        My son, Ben Heuertz, had a solution and <br />
        <span class="font-semibold">The Skinny Platform was born.</span>
      </p>
      <QuotationMark id="rightQuote" fill="currentColor" class="absolute -right-4 -bottom-4" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTAButton action="schedule-call" label="Connect with Ben" class="mt-24 mb-48" />
</div>
